# Animated Landing Page

A modern landing page inspired by SaaS-style UI designs.  
Includes animation effects using JavaScript and Canvas API.

## 📌 Features

- Responsive navigation bar
- Hero section with call-to-action buttons
- Canvas-based illustrations
- Floating animations and particle effects
- Modern UI structure

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)
- Canvas API

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Open the HTML file in a modern web browser.
2. Resize the browser window to see responsive behavior.
3. Observe animated canvas illustrations.

## 🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice:
- Responsive layouts
- UI structuring
- JavaScript animations
- Canvas drawing and rendering

